{"tid":647613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［英國疏忽照顧老人案］蘋果網民：子女無責任照顧父母","createTime":"2018-04-30T03:57:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T04:39:44.000Z","uid":14075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"feaa3a23c4a319100281d9cf2c7b934f8bb03499","tid":647613,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T03:57:33.000Z","msg":"見到d人討論呢個問題都幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/posts/10156688571607448\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fposts%2F10156688571607448&d=o%2B%2Ft6ZNhMNaLeTnMtccsFZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=0f9b94b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/posts/10156688571607448</a><br />\n<br />\n英國一名女律師因故意疏忽罪被判入獄，其母在家中沙發去世時全身滿佈糞便，身上的衣服十年沒有換過，瘦弱得只有39公斤。諷刺的是，這位律師竟然專門處理與照顧長者有關的案件。<br />\n<br />\n41歲被告庫爾茨（Emma-Jane Kurtz）是一位事務律師，她被控故意疏忽罪，在牛津刑事法庭被判入獄兩年半，至少要服刑一半時間，才可改為社會服務。<br />\n<br />\n庫爾茨的79歲母親塞西莉（Cecily Kurtz）於2014年被發現在家中死亡，警方指她「由頭到腳趾都被排洩物覆蓋」，體重僅39公斤，逝世時身體屈曲，5日都維持着下巴貼膝蓋的狀態。當醫護人員移走她的遺體時，她身上的衣服也爛掉，而原本是白色的內衣褲都染成深啡色，排洩物糞便等污垢沾滿她的臉、手和腳。<br />\n<br />\n法官羅斯（Peter Ross）指塞西莉是「被留下慢慢等死」，形容其驗屍報告的照片「看似是拍攝自集中營」。法官考慮到有輕微自閉症的被告正接受治療，相信她有同理心，但她沒有再照顧她患有抑鬱症和強迫症的母親。他說：「這是我遇過最令人震驚及令人厭惡的疏忽案件。」"},{"pid":"35f5b8c869a70ef3a3d918138fb0a9900f38d163","tid":647613,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T04:04:54.000Z","msg":"蘋果民討論<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/120336_8ba2283c88bbfc77fee88328073dc008.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F120336_8ba2283c88bbfc77fee88328073dc008.png&h=3fb049eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/120356_e04cb6ca4df1d2e17232c9f391b65f21.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F120356_e04cb6ca4df1d2e17232c9f391b65f21.png&h=2909b298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/120420_d8a5906c5fea90815cdf1def02c79ef6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F120420_d8a5906c5fea90815cdf1def02c79ef6.png&h=da45352a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8da4bcdce898ff061c736e6680165561dcb4ef6","tid":647613,"uid":171058,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T04:15:16.000Z","msg":"有幾多仆街父母就唔知，但仆街仔女就見唔少<br />\n仆街父母，仔女唔理佢地可以理解<br />\n但仆街仔女，父母眠乾睡濕都可以趕佢地訓街，諗唔通"},{"pid":"0078d73ae17c1f583d7c1cb9ba0e974afce23c4a","tid":647613,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T04:20:04.000Z","msg":"上面條友個論證好正 你無日日幫呀媽換衫=十年冇換件衫變屎色都無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb46820b48c317fc9672a5636923b73cae13759","tid":647613,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T04:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/122319_2bf35f0dd8a08a3869dec9ac2927eaff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F122319_2bf35f0dd8a08a3869dec9ac2927eaff.png&h=93ccebaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/122319_e8c8c3bdf4f21ddd5e90064e24f8cd71.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F122319_e8c8c3bdf4f21ddd5e90064e24f8cd71.png&h=942e4222&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n連登五毛究竟有幾多ACC<br />\n<br />\n五毛真係好鐘意扮足球fans</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"50db06b54a83c7859a2eafe3180a987c9ffebb15","tid":647613,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T04:27:21.000Z","msg":"<